{"tid":1523992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】咪中分化撚計！教你哋咩叫核爆都唔割！","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:15:14.000Z","uid":270333,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d193537701d97cebba554845dffa696d0bdb511","tid":1523992,"uid":270333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"有啲手足會好燥，點解搞咁耐唔散水，太子站點解要同廢老嘈，覺得送頭？大家有呢種情緒好正常，只有當手足係自己人，先會心痛，但咁就好易中分化撚嘅挑撥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋屌之前諗下，如果自己都會暴躁會忍唔到把口，又點樣去要求前線手足冷靜？佢哋經歷緊面對緊嘅嘢，分分鐘更加差。<br />\n<br />\n啱啊，佢哋而家情緒主導啊，好多手足EQ低、一點就著，大家指出咗問題所在，然後呢？屌鳩佢哋就解決咗？<br />\n<br />\n除非本身性格好撚好撚理智，如果唔係，現場前線好易情緒上腦，但講真，冷靜嘅人，就好難不顧一切衝上去做前線。<br />\n<br />\n問心吖，要前線手足兼齊勇氣、冷靜、態度好、聽指揮同體力好，仲要顧全大局同民意，真心公平咩？冇得又要馬兒好 又要馬兒不吃草架？佢哋冇training 過架，呢三個月先臨危受命架，你哋想點要求佢哋完美？<br />\n<br />\n但運動確實需要改正同進步，所以緊記「唔完美，可接受，會改善」，比起用「百屌成材」嘅方式，可以更加理性客觀去講，或者用體諒嘅角度出發，盡量講建議而唔係責罵。<br />\n<br />\n好似太子咁，其實係廢老打記者先，再趕手足落車，坦白講，黑警已經入埋黨鐵控制室，呢班車走得切，下班車都會出事，但手足確實可以更快手，唔洗花咁多時間係條廢老到。<br />\n<br />\n但與其講「屌你哋班友累街坊啊」，不如試下講「班黑警咁仆街大家都好嬲，不過都要提防下，遇到藍絲就唔好浪費時間同佢哋嘈喇，一係打佢一身即走。」<br />\n<br />\n呢啲時候，指責式嘅「百屌成材」只會增加壓力，令手足情緒更加爆煲，更令對家藉機分化成功，唔非和勇，大家都係手足，所以互相體諒好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋都唔好隨便話人分化撚，有啲真係太心痛手足被捕，所以關心者亂啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得啊，不分化、不割蓆、不指責！<br />\n香港人團結一心一齊贏啊！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf17f0d3a2d8f2fb684e1d334e37747aa50483a","tid":1523992,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"dea9c8525062d62fff1a2457d6b86138fc443682","tid":1523992,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:42.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=7af2ccd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=13f29979\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=e4f274bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4eb9dda74bf0fa32b24d8df9cee9d8bf2a1c561e","tid":1523992,"uid":8730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2DpW54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2DpW54.jpg&h=aff9aac3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b193e1110ac07306eb6acd963bc1b83e64fef2a8","tid":1523992,"uid":6561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"聽日機場見"},{"pid":"e14bfc77eca1a148328d426196adcb91a4504d83","tid":1523992,"uid":273585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心痛"},{"pid":"2d0e62a19efa82944e622f41738bd49fb855ef96","tid":1523992,"uid":270333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:33:28